quote: We make our own destiny, not because we can see the road ahead, but because we cannot see the road ahead. It is the road, the motion, the forward movement, that takes us to ourselves.
quote_letters: WE MAKE OUR OWN DESTINY NOT BECAUSE WE CAN SEE THE ROAD AHEAD BUT BECAUSE WE CANNOT SEE THE ROAD AHEAD IT IS THE ROAD THE MOTION THE FORWARD MOVEMENT THAT TAKES US TO OURSELVES
